headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ & RP on The Bunker Series
content: The best fun is underground. In the case of the Bunker Series, we mean that literally: head deep under the earth's crust and shoot it out in a high-tech shelter built to withstand a thermonuclear Judgement Day. What's not relaxing about that? To sweeten the deal, all subterranean modes included in the Bunker Series are dishing out double the usual payout to all combatants.
